#BaselBAE | Celebrating our Creative Icons 

Over the next few days we will be rolling out our presenting artist for Basel BAE 

Introducing Our first Artist Melissa Mitchell Of @abeillecreations 

—-

Melissa is A Miami Native, Graduate of @famu_1887 and self taught artist 

Since founding her own business, Abeille Creations in 2016, she has created 500 large-scale art pieces, 40 murals and has been featured in @forbes @voguemagazine and @essence Magazines.

A Better Life by Abeille Creations (ABL) is a wearable art & custom design house, founded by Melissa A. Mitchell in 2019. ABL’s company focus shifted to creating an art collecting experience through apparel. Each piece created is vibrant, memorable, and full of energy. Year after year, collections are produced in limited quantities and then discontinued to preserve the value of the artistic designs. Melissa uses ABL to educate people about Art, while transferring hope, confidence, and awareness.

It was an honor to attend the first @caribmusicawards 

Special thanks to @wyclefjean the host for the special invite. 

Some people see things in us that we may not. This event United people from all the Caribbean! When @wyclefjean told me to attend I thought it was just another work day an an awards. 

Quickly realize it was deeper then that. It was about keeping all the island United and seeing the visions that the organizers of this event have, and seeing how @lexpromotions can support and contribute for future years to come ! 

This awards show is set to be the next Grammys of the Caribean industry ! Making a promise to support @caribmusicawards
@caribbeanelitemagazine on next years event! 

Congrats to all the winners !!!!!! 
See you next year!! 
Drop your flags in the comment.  We are one Caribbean. 🇭🇹
